channel.description:

[size=24pt]WARNING[/size] I'm releasing this because it got leaked by a developer. He came just to troll and to steal our work. Now, few idiots are selling it. So, be aware. This is the current version. [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/TrCUI.png[/img][/ADMIN]
Download: https://dl.dropbox.com/u/18645949/Release.rar
[*][url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/rhubarb/]Rhubarb[/url] | [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=511718]Int Bauk[/url] [*][url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/atomicint_/]AtomicInt_[/url] | [url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=516337]AtomicInt_[/url] [*][url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/compass_/]Compass_[/url] | [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=454285]artem543[/url]
[size=18pt]Features[/size] [*]Super stable [*]Netty networking [*]Re-package of classes [*]Automatic double experience weekend [*]Good combat system [*]EP system with correct automatic updating interface (red, yellow, green) [*]Randomized loots according to your EP level [*]Slayer point system [*]Fully working woodcutting - with stumps, nests, random events [*]Fully working runecrafting - including talismans [*]Fully working fishing - correct timers, interfaces and additional rock tails added to the database [*]Fully working cooking - burning, correct timers, interfaces and additional rock tails added to the database [*]Fully working herblore - cleaning herbs, creation of potions, etcetera [*]Fully working pest control - timers, interfaces, npc yelling, etcetera [*]Fully working recipe for distaster - updating glove interface, all rounds, hint icons, etcetera [*]Fully working warriors guild - floors, cyclops's, armours, etcetera [*]Fully working fight pits - updating interface, winner, perfect mapdata, etcetera [*]Fully working puzzles - with hints [*]One of the bests fullscreen & resizablescreen [*]Gameframe switcher [474-508-525] [*]Clean cache [*]Cache packed sprites [*]Netty networking has been FULLY implemented [*]Updated walking entities [*]Very stable [*]Process has been cleaned, loads! [*]Methods have been improved conventionally [*]Were now using the Task and TaskScheduler system - for our events [*]All synchronization has been deleted [*]Cache packed over 100 sprites. Only interfaces left. Cleaned client & cache. [*]Adding more information..
